"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-olympian-singh-sets-new-record\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now KATHMANDU, August 18: Olympian Gaurika Singh set two new national records in women's 200m freestyle and 50m butterfly events on the first day of the 20th National Swimming Championship on Thursday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 45, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999973533057083, \"rank\": 2.64670138674861e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 59, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaurika_Singh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gaurika Singh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaurika_Singh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaurika_Singh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"KATHMANDU\", \"from\": 14, \"to\": 23}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 25, \"to\": 31}, {\"ngram\": \"two new national records\", \"from\": 63, \"to\": 87}, {\"ngram\": \"women's 200m freestyle\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 113}, {\"ngram\": \"butterfly events\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 138}, {\"ngram\": \"the first day\", \"from\": 142, \"to\": 155}, {\"ngram\": \"the 20th National Swimming Championship\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 198}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 202, \"to\": 210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the championship being organized by Nepal Swimming Association at the International Sports Complex, Satdobato, Tribhuvan Army Club's Singh shattered the records held by Sofia Shah in both women's 200m freestyle and the 50m butterfly event.Singh completed the 200m distance in two minutes and 11.94 seconds and smashed Shah's record of two minutes and 13.22 seconds.\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 253, \"e